      • INITIAL_POOL_SIZE

        private static int INITIAL_POOL_SIZE
        The connection pool size. This should be as small as possible, and not smaller than the maximum number of concurrent threads. A larger size means fewer clients can have the application open at the same time, limiting the concurrent active userbase
